Package: xsstrike
Version: 3.1.6
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/s0md3v/XSStrike
Description: Advanced XSS Detection and Exploitation Suite
 XSStrike is a Cross Site Scripting detection suite equipped with multiple
 hand-written parsers, an intelligent payload generator, a powerful fuzzing
 engine and an incredibly fast crawler. Instead of injecting payloads and
 checking for reflections, XSStrike analyses responses with multiple parsers
 and then crafts payloads that are guaranteed to work by the context.
 Features:
 - Context-aware payload generation
 - Multiple HTML parsers
 - Powerful fuzzing engine
 - Fast crawler
 - Blind XSS support
 - WAF detection and evasion
